comments: Professor Amicone is not only hot as well, but she is an awesome teacher who knows her stuff inside and out. She is very challenging, but you will not regret taking her class, if you truly want to be more fluent in the language. Profesora, if you read this, I will miss you so much! Gracias para todo :)

An excellent professor if you are serious about learning Spanish. She is clear and is always around for extended assistance. She does not mess around in class, gets right to the point. She knows how to make Spanish understandable and Professor Amicone raised me up in becoming more fluent in the language.
